p.k: Emily is having her own private dance party in Alexis’ living room and making a complete mess! Emily is carefree, she dances around the living room in red booty shorts, fishnets, and Alexis’ stolen boa! Emily is staying with Alexis temporarily and (spoiler) she doesn’t have a lot of respect for cleanliness. Alexis comes home and busts Emily dancing in the living room – the room looks like a pigsty, but Alexis has an idea of how Emily can make it up to her.
